---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Partners" description="Technology partner program. Integrate Clarifid with Socure, Sift, SEON, Jumio, Signifyd.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-normal text-white md:text-5xl">Partners</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-xl text-slate-400">
      We operate as a Technology Partner/OEM. Our partner programs are built for the missing module—explainable fraud intelligence—that platforms embed or resell.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-slate-800/50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-normal text-white md:text-3xl">Priority partnership targets</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-6">
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-white">Socure — RiskOS</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-400">XAI module for lending-specific transparency in RiskOS. Natural-language Reasoning Reports for every flag, reducing manual review time by 40% in mortgage and tenant screening.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-white">SEON — Strategic Alliance</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-400">Lending-native fraud data enrichment layer. Mortgage-specific fraud logic that embeds directly into the Strategic Alliance track.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-white">Sift — Technology Partner</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-400">Explainable rules engine reducing false positives by 30%.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-white">Jumio — Technology Partner</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-400">Anti-injection deepfake defense for financial onboarding. Hardware-anchored verification adds Injection Attack protection for high-value financial onboarding.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-white">Signifyd — Platform/Integration Partner</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-400">Post-approval monitoring for lending fraud signals.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-slate-800/50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-normal text-white md:text-3xl">Partnership benefits</h2>
      <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-slate-400">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-amber-400">•</span>
          <span>Self-serve API key generation and sandbox environment</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-amber-400">•</span>
          <span>mTLS certificate provisioning</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-amber-400">•</span>
          <span>Per-partner rule configuration and threshold adjustments</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-amber-400">•</span>
          <span>Configurable webhooks for decision alerts and threshold breaches</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-amber-400">•</span>
          <span>Data residency controls for PIPEDA/CCPA/GDPR</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-slate-800/50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-normal text-white md:text-3xl">Entry strategy</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-amber-400">Phase 1: Partner-First</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Sell as OEM/white-label module. Per-transaction fees or revenue share. Immediate distribution via partner customer base.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-amber-400">Phase 2: Direct + Partner</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Launch direct API for mid-market. Self-serve onboarding, transparent pricing. Case studies from partner deployments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-amber-400">Phase 3: Platform Expansion</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Post-origination monitoring. Canadian market. International compliance modules. Fraud-loss guarantee program.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-amber-500 px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-slate-950 hover:bg-amber-400 transition-colors">
          Start a partnership
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
